::Cygnus::
    He landed to rest his weary wings and began walking around.  He could 
tell from the foliage he was somewhere in Maine or near there.  He sends out 
a message instead of searching for more bots he would let them find him 
"Hello.  This is Cygnus.  I am looking for others.  Someone please find me.  
I'm a little lost."
